Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:03:00.49,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3cFFFFFF\bord3\blur2.5\1aFF}世界也可以轻易颠覆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:07.41,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3cFFFFFF\bord3\blur2.5\1aFF}前路充满未知  只需要笑脸相迎
